Job responsibilities 

  Handled all phone calls with a pleasant and professional telephone voice.
  Maintained a tidy reception area.
  Maintained cleanliness of all gym equipment.
  Ensured front desk was well attended at all times.
  Coordinated all booking of class schedules, training and orientation.

Requirement 

  Must be able to work shift hours : 6 45am to 2 45pm OR 2:15pm to 10:15pm
  Have good command of english 
  Good team player 
  Able to handle booking software, emails, word, excel , powerpoint 
  Minimum Higher Nitec / Diploma 
  Resourceful and independant 
